Package: mlr3oml
Title: Connector Between 'mlr3' and 'OpenML'
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R:
    person("Michel", "Lang", , "michellang@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9754-0393"))
Description: Provides an interface to 'OpenML.org' to list and download
    machine learning data and tasks. Data and tasks can be automatically
    converted to 'mlr3' tasks. For a more sophisticated interface which
    also allows uploading experiments, see the 'OpenML' package.
License: LGPL-3
URL: https://mlr3oml.mlr-org.com, https://github.com/mlr-org/mlr3oml
BugReports: https://github.com/mlr-org/mlr3oml/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
